query:
SELECT 
  race_date,
  COUNT(*) as odds_count,
  COUNT(DISTINCT stadium_code) as stadiums,
  COUNT(DISTINCT race_number) as races,
  MIN(scraped_at) as first_scraped,
  MAX(scraped_at) as last_scraped
FROM odds_history 
WHERE race_date >= '2026-01-01'
GROUP BY race_date
ORDER BY race_date DESC
LIMIT 10;
